FT  21 APR 93 / Home move plans
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
ABOUT 1.7m houseowners expect to move within the next 12 months, compared
with 1.3m who moved last year, according to a report published yesterday by
the Alliance &amp; Leicester Building Society. Mr Peter White, Alliance &amp;
Leicester chief executive, said the backlog of housing demand was 'like a
dam waiting to burst'.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
