<HEADLINE>
FT  20 APR 93 / UK Company News: Rentokil makes Pounds 1.75m acquisition
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Rentokil has acquired the facilities maintenance division of John Lelliott,
the building company which is in receivership, for a maximum Pounds 1.75m
cash.
In the year to June 30 1992 the business had turnover of Pounds 6.49m and
profits of Pounds 440,000.
