FT  20 APR 93 / Machine tool company 'saved'
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE managing director of Dean Smith &amp; Grace has saved part of the West
Yorkshire-based machine tool company from closure by acquiring the spares,
service and rebuilding activities from Monarch Machine Tool, the US parent
company.
